title: Default values are not displayed in Show Report Parameters dialog
OB: When viewing the Show Report Parameters dialog, the default values of the report parameters are not shown.
EB: When viewing the Show Report Parameters dialog, the default values of the report parameters should be displayed.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Create multiple report parameters. 2. Set default values for these parameters. 3. Drag the parameters to the Layout area. 4. Open the Show Report Parameters dialog and observe that the default values are not displayed.
